trackMetadata.trackName: 革命道中 - On The Way

highlights.text: “革命道中 - On The Way” by AiNA THE END is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Finland, up 7 spots at #85.
“Mun ihminen” by ELLIMEI has been on Viral Songs Finland the longest, at 148 days straight.
At The Gates has the most spots on Viral Songs Finland. “Slaughter Of The Soul” is the highest at #24.
“Voiko enkelitkin eksyä” by Haloo Helsinki! is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Finland at #2.
